ion":{"start":{"line":14,"column":14,"offset":414},"end":{"line":14,"column":39,"offset":439},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131311"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131435","id":"zettel.20260420131435","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":14,"offset":1823},"end":{"line":42,"column":39,"offset":1848},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131311"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","id":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":146,"column":3,"offset":9096},"end":{"line":146,"column":28,"offset":9121},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131311"}],"anchors":{"gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Gagasan","value":"gagasan","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"mengapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Mengapa Ini Penting","value":"mengapa-ini-penting","line":21,"column":0,"depth":2},"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain":{"type":"header","text":"Hubungan ke Zettel Lain","value":"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":32,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"kolaborasi-manusia-multi-hari-memindahkan-memori-kerja-ke-dokumen-bersama\">Kolaborasi manusia multi-hari memindahkan memori kerja ke dokumen bersama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kolaborasi-manusia-multi-hari-memindahkan-memori-kerja-ke-dokumen-bersama\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"gagasan\">Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Dalam kolaborasi manusia, tim yang bekerja pada fitur selama beberapa hari secara alami memindahkan memori kerja penting ke dokumen bersama.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Di sini, \"dokumen bersama\" berarti artifact yang tim gunakan sebagai konteks kerja bersama: issue/ticket, PR description, shared design doc, spesifikasi fitur, atau catatan keputusan yang terus diperbarui.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"mengapa-ini-penting\">Mengapa Ini Penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#mengapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Ini memberi legitimasi praktis untuk context anchoring AI. Kalau engineer sudah memakai dokumen bersama untuk memelihara konteks antar rekan, maka ide yang sama untuk AI bukanlah abstraksi jauh.</p>\n<p>Kalimat ini ditulis di sini untuk menegaskan bahwa kita sedang bicara tentang pola kolaborasi nyata, bukan teori. Contoh dokumen bersama menunjukkan bagaimana konteks kerja memang dipindahkan dari kepala satu orang ke artifact bersama yang bisa dibaca dan dilanjutkan oleh orang lain — dan oleh AI.</p>\n<h2 id=\"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\">Hubungan ke Zettel Lain<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Mendukung <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — klaim diambil dari Paragraf 1.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131310\">Percakapan AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan</a> — tesis utama bahwa chat AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — Paragraf 1</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #a03623;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.zettel\">zettel</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-collaboration (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f0944d;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.knowledge-management\">knowledge-management</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">context-anchoring (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131310\">Percakapan AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131312\">AI memory tools sekarang kebanyakan project-level, bukan feature-level</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131400\">Kecemasan menutup chat adalah indikator context leakage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131401\">Erosi konteks AI adalah isu arsitektural, bukan bug acak</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131402\">Context window besar tetap cepat habis dalam praktik engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131403\">Posisi informasi memengaruhi recall; tengah konteks adalah zona rawan hilang</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131404\">Dalam erosi konteks, why hilang sebelum what</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131405\">Kalau medium lupa, pindahkan memori ke luar medium itu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131406\">Summarization otomatis menyelamatkan what, bukan why</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131407\">Alignment tanpa persistence tetap rapuh</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131408\">Context anchoring adalah durability layer untuk alignment manusia-AI</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131409\">Decision context harus menjadi external state, bukan jejak chat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131410\">Project context dan feature context punya fungsi berbeda</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131411\">Priming document adalah memori stabil level proyek</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131412\">Feature document adalah memori dinamis level pekerjaan yang sedang berlangsung</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131413\">Agar efektif, AI butuh dua lapis konteks: fondasi stabil dan riwayat lokal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131414\">Membaca codebase tidak sama dengan memahami keputusan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131415\">Code menyimpan outcome; reasoning dan rejected history tidak tampak di sana</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131416\">Feature document lebih semantik-padatan dan token-efisien daripada mengekstrak reasoning dari kode</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131417\">Context anchoring untuk AI adalah versi kontemporer dari kebutuhan yang melahirkan ADR</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131418\">Feature document adalah ADR hidup selama proses, bukan catatan pasca-fakta</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131419\">Feature document bisa jadi jembatan antara kerja harian dan dokumentasi formal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131420\">Context anchoring adalah infrastruktur koordinasi tim, bukan hanya memori individu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131421\">Dokumen adalah mekanisme persistence yang menggantikan keterbatasan model</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131422\">Solusi ini bisa dipasang ke contoh praktis, bukan sekadar teori</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131423\">Begitu keputusan desain terkristal, pindahkan ke dokumen bersama alasannya</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131424\">Feature document yang efektif itu ringkas dan operasional</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131425\">Struktur minimal feature document jelas dan praktis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131426\">Nilai anchoring muncul saat sesi baru bisa warm start</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131427\">Maintenance dokumen harus menempel ke ritme kerja alami</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131428\">Feature document memaksa reasoning menjadi lebih jelas</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131429\">Feature document mengompresi hari kerja menjadi konteks yang bisa diakses ulang cepat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131430\">Context anchoring adalah alat yang harus dikalibrasi, bukan default universal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131431\">Kebutuhan anchoring naik seiring durasi, revisit, dan jumlah orang</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131432\">Nilai anchoring ditentukan oleh overhead dokumentasi versus biaya kehilangan konteks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131433\">Keinginan mempertahankan chat adalah indikator anchoring belum cukup</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131434\">Chat adalah medium berpikir; dokumen adalah medium penyimpanan keputusan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131435\">Keberhasilan context anchoring diukur dari murahnya restart</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"seeds":{"dendron.templates":{}},"enableFullHierarchyNoteTitle":false},"preview":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enableFrontmatterTags":true,"enableHashesForFMTags":false,"enablePrettyRefs":true,"enableKatex":true,"automaticallyShowPreview":false},"publishing":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enablePrettyRefs":true,"enableKatex":true,"copyAssets":true,"siteHierarchies":["root"],"writeStubs":true,"siteRootDir":"docs","seo":{"title":"Sotoy","description":"Personal knowledge space about anything I learn. Notes, knowledge, and ideas from me.","author":"Zeihan Aulia","twitter":"zeihanaulia","image":{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/502375255256485888/1UYtt7PT_400x400.jpeg","alt":"Software Engineer, "}},"github":{"enableEditLink":true,"editLinkText":"Edit this page on GitHub","editBranch":"main","editViewMode":"tree"},"enableSiteLastModified":true,"enableFrontmatterTags":true,"enableHashesForFMTags":false,"enableRandomlyColoredTags":true,"enableTaskNotes":true,"enablePrettyLinks":true,"searchMode":"lookup","assetsPrefix":"/sotoy","siteUrl":"https://zeihanaulia.github.io","duplicateNoteBehavior":{"action":"useVault","payload":["vault-private","vault","dendron.templates"]},"siteFaviconPath":"favicon.ico","siteIndex":"root"}}},"__N_SSG":true}